Package venice.hub.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgumentParser
    Defines command line arguments and how to parse them.
    Configuration
    Parses command line arguments and provides the configuration data for the other components.
    ConnectionConverter
    Converts an object into a Connection.
    TTE
    Holds a data item with value, sensor name, data type and timestamp and provides methods for calculating and comparing delays.
    TTEBuffer
    A buffer for TTE objects with random access, to enable fast seeking in log files.
    TTEBufferedReader
    Doing the real work for the DiskReader, reads data from file, parses it into TTE items and caches them, until DiskReader will take them.
    TTEQueue
    A singleton queue that stores data read by VeniceReader objects and provide it for VeniceWriter objects, with delaying items by use of the timestamp.
    XIOParserValidator
    Provides validation of a command line argument for XIO parser name.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Configuration.Connection
    The possible connections for data sources and targets.
